errors.error_description: Incorrect installation order by running docker-compose up without proper setup steps first
correction_candidates: Step-by-step installation instructions are available in our [documentation](https://docs.librephotos.com/docs/installation/standard-install)
To get started, first clone the repository, then configure your environment, and finally run docker-compose up.
To get started, download the Docker Compose file, configure your settings, then run docker-compose up.
To get started, ensure Docker is installed, clone the repository, configure environment variables, then run docker-compose up.
errors.golden_answer: Step-by-step installation instructions are available in our [documentation](https://docs.librephotos.com/docs/installation/standard-install)
